{"text_id":112009,"tokens":["The"," opportunity"," to"," participate"," in"," extracurricular"," activities"," and"," sports"," is"," a"," vital"," aspect"," of"," the"," overall"," educational"," experience","."," These"," activities"," provide"," students"," with"," the"," chance"," to"," develop"," new"," skills",","," build"," relationships",","," and"," engage"," in"," physical"," fitness","."," However",","," financial"," barriers"," often"," prevent"," some"," students"," from"," taking"," part"," in"," these"," enriching"," opportunities","."," It"," is"," essential"," that"," schools"," and"," communities"," provide"," alternative"," options"," for"," students"," who"," cannot"," afford"," to"," participate",".","\n\n","Extra","curricular"," activities"," and"," sports"," often"," require"," students"," to"," pay"," participation"," fees",","," purchase"," equipment"," or"," uniforms",","," and"," cover"," transportation"," costs","."," For"," families"," who"," are"," already"," struggling"," to"," make"," ends"," meet",","," these"," additional"," expenses"," can"," be"," prohibitive","."," As"," a"," result",","," many"," students"," are"," unable"," to"," take"," part"," in"," activities"," that"," could"," have"," a"," significant"," impact"," on"," their"," personal"," and"," academic"," growth",".","\n\n","Providing"," alternative"," options"," for"," students"," who"," cannot"," afford"," to"," participate"," in"," traditional"," extracurricular"," activities"," and"," sports"," is"," crucial","."," These"," alternatives"," can"," take"," many"," forms",","," such"," as"," community","-","based"," programs",","," scholarships",","," and"," sliding","-","scale"," fee"," structures","."," By"," offering"," a"," range"," of"," options",","," schools"," and"," communities"," can"," ensure"," that"," all"," students"," have"," the"," opportunity"," to"," engage"," in"," enriching"," activities",","," regardless"," of"," their"," financial"," situation","